---
---

<footer id="contact" class="w-full bg-[#050505] border-t border-white/5 py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-6">
          Καθαρός Κώδικας,<br />
          <span class="text-zinc-500">Αθόρυβη Εκτέλεση.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 mb-10 max-w-md">
          Κάθε project είναι μια ευκαιρία για βελτιστοποίηση και δημιουργία αξίας. 
          Ας συζητήσουμε για την επόμενη ιδέα σας.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="mailto:contact@example.com" class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 hover:border-indigo-500 transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"></path></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 hover:border-indigo-500 transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"></rect><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="p-3 rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 hover:border-indigo-500 transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"></path><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"></path></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-500 opacity-20 blur"></div>
        <div class="relative rounded-xl bg-[#0d0d0d] border border-white/10 p-6 font-mono text-sm shadow-2xl">
          <div class="flex gap-1.5 mb-4">
            <div class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div>
            <div class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div>
            <div class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <p class="text-zinc-500"><span class="text-indigo-400">const</span> project = {"{"}</p>
            <p class="pl-4 text-zinc-400">name: <span class="text-green-400">'Next Big Idea'</span>,</p>
            <p class="pl-4 text-zinc-400">status: <span class="text-green-400">'Ready'</span>,</p>
            <p class="pl-4 text-zinc-400">stack: [<span class="text-yellow-400">'Astro'</span>, <span class="text-yellow-400">'Tailwind'</span>],</p>
            <p class="pl-4 text-zinc-400">coffee: <span class="text-indigo-400">true</span></p>
            <p class="text-zinc-500">{"}"};</p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-500 font-italic">// Ας ξεκινήσουμε!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-zinc-600 text-sm">
      <p>© 2026 Architect. Με σεβασμό στον κώδικα.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-8">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-zinc-400">Privacy</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-zinc-400">Terms</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
